{"tid":432801,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"FIFA18 Pro club 招右翼","createTime":"2017-10-12T00:15:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-27T14:39:58.000Z","uid":131680,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"579b137bc1d2d8750bbdd7c9116b5cd74d2a721b","tid":432801,"uid":131680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T00:15:16.000Z","msg":"本隊現招一名 右翼<br />\n<br />\n球隊現時排名: D4<br />\n現役隊員: 5名<br />\n陣式: 4231<br />\n開波時間: 10pm - 01:00am 左右<br />\n球隊踢法: 防反, 少上腳, 快速反擊, 現位接應, 多交波, 少扭波<br />\n球隊目標: 輕鬆玩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n右翼要求:<br />\n1. 有位置感, 不亂走入中路<br />\n2. 勤於回防, 要幫電腦RB補位防守<br />\n3. 與CAM撞墻/overlap走位<br />\n4. 見ST有位就 即cross or 3角<br />\n5. 配合球隊踢法<br />\n6. 有右翼經驗者優先考慮<br />\n7. 不收part time<br />\n8. 入party 吹下水<br />\n<br />\n有興趣 可留psn, 謝謝。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"762382e684f59321295c7ae82dd6c5e133dca40c","tid":432801,"uid":131680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T06:45:37.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"701e6c3652eb626ceea1e2379bc59e5d2b0a1a02","tid":432801,"uid":131680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T13:29:25.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a25362651f523644910dd308328f25a72e39fd23","tid":432801,"uid":107101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T14:51:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdd151aedc342ce9cd79ddd941e182f6e6e9afd3","tid":432801,"uid":131680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T04:51:18.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1193e9b3066f0d2a8cb7308238e383631d4bfa5c","tid":432801,"uid":117097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T08:51:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"